:"a contrivance, i.e. (concretely) a texture, machine, or (abstractly) intention, plan (whether bad, a plot; or good, advice)","kjv_def":"cunning (work), curious work, device(-sed), imagination, invented, means, purpose, thought.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"thought(28x), device(12x), purpose(6x), work(3x), imaginations(3x), cunning(1x), devised(1x), invented(1x), means(1x)"},"H4285":{"id":"H4285","lemma":"מַחְשָׁךְ","translit":"machshâk","pron":"makh-shawk'","derivation":"from H2821 (חָשַׁךְ);","strongs_def":"darkness; concretely, a dark place","kjv_def":"dark(-ness, place).","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"darkness(4x), dark(1x)"},"H4286":{"id":"H4286","lemma":"מַחְשֹׂף","translit":"machsôph","pron":"makh-sofe'","derivation":"from H2834 (חָשַׂף);","strongs_def":"a peeling","kjv_def":"made appear.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"appear(1x)"},"H4287":{"id":"H4287","lemma":"מַחַת","translit":"Machath","pron":"makh'-ath","derivation":"probably from H4229 (מָחָה); erasure;","strongs_def":"Machath, the name of two Israelites","kjv_def":"Mahath."},"H4288":{"id":"H4288","lemma":"מְחִתָּה","translit":"mᵉchittâh","pron":"mekh-it-taw'","derivation":"from H2846 (חָתָה);","strongs_def":"properly, a dissolution; concretely, a ruin, or (abstractly) consternation","kjv_def":"destruction, dismaying, ruin, terror.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"destruction(7x), terror(2x), ruin(1x), dismaying(1x)"},"H4289":{"id":"H4289","lemma":"מַחְתָּה","translit":"machtâh","pron":"makh-taw'","derivation":"the same as H4288 (מְחִתָּה) in the sense of removal;","strongs_def":"a pan for live coals","kjv_def":"censer, firepan, snuffdish.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"censer(15x), firepans(4x), snuffdishes(3x)"},"H4290":{"id":"H4290","lemma":"מַחְתֶּרֶת","translit":"machtereth","pron":"makh-teh'-reth","derivation":"from H2864 (חָתַר);","strongs_def":"a burglary; figuratively, unexpected examination","kjv_def":"breaking up, secret search.","pos":"masculine noun"},"H4291":{"id":"H4291","lemma":"